column2: Tencent Music Entertainment Group engages in the provision of online music entertainment platform. The company is headquartered in Shenzhen, Guangdong and currently employs 3,041 full-time employees. The firm's platform comprises online music, online karaoke and music-centric live streaming services, supported by content offerings, technology and data. The firm's main platform includes QQ Music, Kugou Music, Kuwo Music, WeSing, Kugou Live, Kuwo Live and others.
